OL,3,COver 100 firefighters tackle blaze in
OL,4,COmagh with person airlifted to hospital
OL,6,FOne person has been taken to hospital
OL,7,Fby Air Ambulance following a large
OL,8,Ffire at an industrial estate in Omagh.
OL,10,FEmergency services attended the fire
OL,11,Fat the Doogary Industrial Estate on
OL,12,FWednesday morning.
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FService (NIFRS) said over 100
OL,16,Ffirefighters are attending the
OL,17,Fincident after receiving a call after
OL,18,F7AM.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
