CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775077865
OL,3,COver 100 firefighters tackle blaze in
OL,4,COmagh with person airlifted to hospital
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,7,F(NIAS) said one person was taken to
OL,8,FRoyal Victoria Hospital, Belfast
OL,9,Ffollowing treatment at the scene.
OL,11,FThe Bankmore Road is closed at the A5
OL,12,Fand Crevenagh Road junctions.JPolice
OL,13,Fhave advised motorists to seek an
OL,14,Falternative route.
OL,16,FSinn Fein MP Orfhlaith Begley said her
OL,17,F"thoughts are with the individual
OL,18,Finjured due to a fire that has taken
OL,19,Fplace in Boyd Bedding."
OL,26,@xD@GrrxD@Nrg
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
