OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775077865
OL,3,COver 100 firefighters tackle blaze in
OL,4,COmagh with person airlifted to hospital
OL,6,F"I want to commend the emergency
OL,7,Fservices and air ambulance for
OL,8,Fresponding swiftly to this incident.
OL,9,FThere are currently ten fire engines
OL,10,Fdeployed to the scene of this incident.
OL,12,F"I would ask motorists to avoid the
OL,13,FBankmore Road which remains closed at
OL,14,Fthis time," she added.
OL,16,F"I am thinking of all those impacted
OL,17,Fby this incident and hoping they make
OL,18,Fa full and speedy recovery."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
