OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775077865
OL,3,COver 100 firefighters tackle blaze in
OL,4,COmagh with person airlifted to hospital
OL,6,FWest Tyrone DUP MLA Tom Buchanan also
OL,7,Fexpressed concern following the
OL,8,Fincident which he said involved "a
OL,9,Freported dust explosion".
OL,11,F"I want to pay tribute to the swift
OL,12,Fand professional response of the
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland Fire & Rescue Service
OL,14,Fand all emergency personnel who worked
OL,15,Fto bring the situation under control,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
OL,18,F"My immediate thoughts are with
OL,19,Feveryone affected by this incident."
OL,26,@pD@aOUqD@XO]sD@AOUwD@fO]zD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
