CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775077865
OL,3,COver 100 firefighters tackle blaze in
OL,4,COmagh with person airlifted to hospital
OL,6,FNIFRS Western Area Commander David
OL,7,FDoherty said: "The initial call was
OL,8,Freceived at 07:19AM this morning.
OL,10,F"There are currently 15 fire
OL,11,Fappliances, over 100 firefighters, an
OL,12,Faerial appliance, a high volume pump,
OL,13,Ftwo water tankers and a command
OL,14,Fsupport unit in attendance. The
OL,15,Fincident is ongoing.
OL,26,@oD@OOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
