OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775077865
OL,3,COver 100 firefighters tackle blaze in
OL,4,COmagh with person airlifted to hospital
OL,6,F"One casualty was treated by
OL,7,Ffirefighters at the scene and
OL,8,Ftransferred to the care of the
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland Ambulance Service and
OL,10,Ftransported to hospital via Northern
OL,11,FIreland Air Ambulance."
OL,13,FNIAS said they received a call at
OL,14,F07:21AM on Wednesday.
OL,16,FThey said: "NIAS dispatched one
OL,17,Femergency ambulance and the charity
OL,18,FAir Ambulance with HEMS on board, to
OL,19,Fthe scene.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
