OL,3,COver 100 firefighters tackle blaze in
OL,4,COmagh with person airlifted to hospital
OL,6,F"Following assessment and initial
OL,7,Ftreatment at the scene, one person was
OL,8,Ftaken to Royal Victoria Hospital,
OL,9,FBelfast."
